title: 2016 Week 9 review
itunes:title: 2016 Week 9 review
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling, and Gregg Rosenthal – go game-by-game breaking down each Week 9 matchup which included the Colts coming up with a big win at Lambeau over the Packers, and another disappointing showing from the Team of ATL.
